org.hl7.fhir.instance.model

Class Meta

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Base
      • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Element
        • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Type
          • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Meta
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IBase, IBaseDatatype, IBaseHasExtensions, IBaseMetaType, ICompositeType

    public class Meta
extends Type
implements IBaseMetaType
    The metadata about a resource. This is content in the resource that is maintained by the infrastructure. Changes to the content may not always be associated with version changes to the resource.
    See Also:
